{"id": 745, "genre": 1001, "title": "你什么时候看书效率最高？", "description": "看书最高效：把书摊在作业底下随时提防爸妈进来检查的那些时刻。（题图来自：M3）", "record_count": 5076, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194542zEV0hFon6HKDAwyM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-12T12:55:58Z", "options": [{"id": 40960, "content": "手机不在身边的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307463}, {"id": 40961, "content": "安静的环境，充足的照明，大大的书桌，舒服的椅子，没有WiFi。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121008}, {"id": 40962, "content": "妈蛋，明天考宏观经济学了，现在的我简直头脑中转的像马达", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365683}, {"id": 43010, "content": "明天就要考试的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434789}, {"id": 40963, "content": "妈蛋，明天考宏观经济学了，现在的我简直头脑中转的像马达", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365683}, {"id": 40965, "content": "有目标有计划的时候 在图书馆的时候 气氛好的时候 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168523}, {"id": 43525, "content": "睡觉的时候留在梦中看?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 88241}, {"id": 45573, "content": "没有手机没有电视，家里那些宠物都没来烦我的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 40966, "content": "熬过要死要活的开头之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387890}, {"id": 40967, "content": "半夜看小说的时候，明明很困，就是想看，所以哗啦哗啦翻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115503}, {"id": 41223, "content": "考试前一天 社会主义好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78286}, {"id": 43527, "content": "想睡觉的时候......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 88241}, {"id": 40968, "content": "考试前一天的深夜，一定要深夜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416617}, {"