 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 44315, "content": "有实际需求时，有针对性的查找书籍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442060}, {"id": 40988, "content": "明天有事要起床，或者明天要考试，反正就是该睡觉、该学习该干嘛的时候。拿起本无关紧要的书，就放不下了。感觉好像是一种逃避的疏解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309836}, {"id": 40990, "content": "氛围宁静的晚上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 43295, "content": "在一个光亮又不刺眼，只有我一人，和无尽的音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433269}, {"id": 40992, "content": "当周围的人都在看书的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291952}, {"id": 44320, "content": "有实际需求时，有针对性的查找书籍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442060}, {"id": 40993, "content": "心血来潮的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 420879}, {"id": 40994, "content": "喜欢它的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416801}, {"id": 40995, "content": "晚上入睡前，看书最安静", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394831}, {"id": 40996, "content": "考试前一天能看完一整本书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181984}, {"id": 40997, "content": "如果我说\"没有\"?好伤心，自己都想哭了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163696}, {"id": 41509, "content": "上厕所的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425180}, {"id": 42533, "content": "中学时英语课前课间十分钟，因为一上课就会听写单词", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431098}, {"id": 41254, "content": "睡前看书最有效率 而且最专注", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181443}, {"id": 46375, "content": "什么时候都不高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453659}, {"id": 41000, "content": "坐长途火车时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect":